  "text": "## Summary\n\nInventory of all Go source files in Kubernetes v1.32.0 that reference the `ScoreExtensions` interface and related symbols for the planned rename to `ScoreNormalizer`.\n\n## Interface Definition\nThe `ScoreExtensions` interface is defined in **pkg/scheduler/framework/interface.go** (lines 597-603) and represents extended Score plugin functionality with a single method: `NormalizeScore()`. The `ScorePlugin` interface (lines 605-616) contains the accessor method `ScoreExtensions()` (line 615) that returns a `ScoreExtensions` interface or nil.\n\n## Plugin Implementations\nNine plugins under **pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/** implement the `ScoreExtensions()` method:\n1. **noderesources/fit.go** - `Fit.ScoreExtensions()` returns nil\n2. **interpodaffinity/scoring.go** - `InterPodAffinity.ScoreExtensions()` returns self (implements `NormalizeScore()`)\n3. **podtopologyspread/scoring.go** - `PodTopologySpread.ScoreExtensions()` returns self (implements `NormalizeScore()`)\n4. **nodeaffinity/node_affinity.go** - `NodeAffinity.ScoreExtensions()` returns self (implements `NormalizeScore()`)\n5. **volumebinding/volume_binding.go** - `VolumeBinding.ScoreExtensions()` returns nil\n6. **imagelocality/image_locality.go** - `ImageLocality.ScoreExtensions()` returns nil\n7. **tainttoleration/taint_toleration.go** - `TaintToleration.ScoreExtensions()` returns self (implements `NormalizeScore()`)\n8. **noderesources/balanced_allocation.go** - `BalancedAllocation.ScoreExtensions()` returns nil\n\n## Runtime Framework\n**pkg/scheduler/framework/runtime/framework.go** contains the `runScoreExtension()` function (lines 1168-1237) that:\n- Calls `ScoreExtensions()` on plugins (lines 1171, 1232, 1235)\n- Uses the `ScoreExtensionNormalize` metric constant (line 1236)\n\n## Metrics\n**pkg/scheduler/metrics/metrics.go** defines the `ScoreExtensionNormalize` constant (line 74) used for tracking plugin duration metrics.\n\n## Testing Framework and Test Plugins\nSeveral test helper plugins implement `ScoreExtensions()`:\n- **pkg/scheduler/testing/framework/fake_plugins.go** - `FakePreScoreAndScorePlugin.ScoreExtensions()`\n- **pkg/scheduler/testing/framework/fake_extender.go** - `node2PrioritizerPlugin.ScoreExtensions()`\n\n## Test Files (19 files total)\nAll test files reference `ScoreExtensions` through either method implementations or direct calls to `ScoreExtensions().NormalizeScore()`:\n\n1. **test/integration/scheduler/plugins/plugins_test.go** - `ScorePlugin` and `ScoreWithNormalizePlugin` test plugins\n2. **pkg/scheduler/schedule_one_test.go** - Multiple test plugins with `ScoreExtensions()` implementations\n3. **pkg/scheduler/framework/runtime/framework_test.go** - Test plugins: `TestScoreWithNormalizePlugin`, `TestScorePlugin`, `TestPlugin`\n4. **pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/interpodaffinity/scoring_test.go** - Calls `ScorePlugin.ScoreExtensions().NormalizeScore()` (lines 813, 976)\n5. **pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/nodeaffinity/node_affinity_test.go** - Calls `ScorePlugin.ScoreExtensions().NormalizeScore()` (line 1224)\n6. **pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/tainttoleration/taint_toleration_test.go** - Calls `ScorePlugin.ScoreExtensions().NormalizeScore()` (line 261)\n\n## Supporting Files\n**pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/helper/normalize_score.go** and **normalize_score_test.go** define and test the `DefaultNormalizeScore()` helper function used by plugins implementing `ScoreExtensions`.\n\n## Total Files Requiring Updates\nAt least **21 files** will require updates to rename `ScoreExtensions` to `ScoreNormalizer` and the associated accessor method from `ScoreExtensions()` to `ScoreNormalizer()`."
